<div class="mx-auto md:w-5/6 w-full flex">
  <div class="mx-auto">
    <% if notice.present? %>
      <p class="py-2 px-3 bg-green-50 mb-5 text-green-500 font-medium rounded-lg inline-block" id="notice"><%= notice %></p>
    <% end %>

    <div data-controller="info-box">
      <div class="info-button">&#x24D8;</div>
      <ul class="info-box">
        <li>Instructor scores show aggregated results for all instructors (Professionals) at the event.
        <li>Scores are compiled across all heats where the instructor danced with their students.
        <li>Results may include total points, average scores, placement counts, or other metrics depending on the scoring system used.
        <li>Page updates automatically during the event when judges enter new scores (live scoring).
        <li>Final scores are available after all heats have been judged and scores entered.
        <li>This public-facing page can be shared with instructors and studios to view results in real-time.
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-bold mt-8 text-4xl pb-5 text-center">Instructor Scores</h1>

    <%= turbo_stream_from "live-scores-#{ENV['RAILS_APP_DB']}" %>
    <%= render partial: "last_update", locals: {action: instructor_scores_path, timestamp: @last_score_update} %>

    <%= render "instructors" %>

    <%= link_to 'Back to summary', summary_event_index_path, class: "ml-2 rounded-lg py-3 px-5 bg-gray-100 inline-block font-medium" %>
  </div>
</div>